{"tid":2293038,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"加拿大通過議案 要求政府禁華為參與 5G 建設","createTime":"2020-11-20T03:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T06:18:47.000Z","uid":28114,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"49300862c67e332b26eb084e925e5d11982e4aa5","tid":2293038,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2805000/2807257/trme-huawei-5g-vision-in-mwc2018_1024_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2805000%2F2807257%2Ftrme-huawei-5g-vision-in-mwc2018_1024_1024_1024.jpg&h=f554f6dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基於國家安全，不少國家都考慮甚至明言放棄使用華為 5G 設備。加拿大在野保守黨動議一項無約束力動議，要求總理杜魯多（Justin Trudeau）對中國採取更強硬的態度，包括正式禁止華為 5G 技術在加拿大使用，最後以 179 票贊成、146 票反對獲通過。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大在野保守黨動議一項無約束力動議，要求總理杜魯多對中國採取更強硬的態度<br />\n最終以 179 票贊成、146 票反對獲通過<br />\n杜魯多一再表示，政府正在靜候加國情治機構給予建議<br />\n<br />\n加拿大在野保守黨提出無約束力動議，稱中國對加拿大利益和價值是一大威脅，並呼籲政府草擬計劃，對抗中國日益增長的外國行動。保守黨黨魁 Erin O'Toole 表示：「我們呼籲自由黨政府徹底鼓起勇氣，對華為在加拿大的 5G 網路參與做出決定。」<br />\n<br />\n五眼聯盟（Five Eyes）中，美國、英國、澳洲和紐西蘭都已採取行動禁用華為 5G 技術，但加拿大政府至今仍未作出任何決定。杜魯多一再表示，政府正在靜候加國情治機構給予建議。<br />\n<br />\n華為加拿大副總裁 Alykhan Velshi 表示，華為支持政府對潛在 5G 供應商的循證審查，並補充表示華為從未收到來自加拿大有關安全漏洞的投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2807257/加拿大通過議案%20%20要求政府禁華為參與%205G%20建設\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2807257%2F%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E8%AD%B0%E6%A1%88%2520%2520%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A6%81%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%25205G%2520%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BQ2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=f7d1e5b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2807257/加拿大通過議案%20%20要求政府禁華為參與%205G%20建設</a>"},{"pid":"751825238ec6fcf559dd6e51a380fda8e3283651","tid":2293038,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:31:24.000Z","msg":"Canada&rsquo;s opposition party urges PM Justin Trudeau to ban Huawei 5G<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/11/19/canada-demans-huawei-5g-ban/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gizmochina.com%2F2020%2F11%2F19%2Fcanada-demans-huawei-5g-ban%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BQ2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=d1509d97\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/11/19/canada-demans-huawei-5g-ban/</a>"},{"pid":"ed0109b9ecbe50676ffe74e6fc28af0f512948bb","tid":2293038,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:33:40.000Z","msg":"Good"},{"pid":"3e76ae0be953cccf0c61c3a9612cb194273f6554","tid":2293038,"uid":147628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515883a4f95674b28d55a7524c1cedc7d2236fa9","tid":2293038,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:45:49.000Z","msg":"146票反對係暗共？"},{"pid":"b4df4c60f2dc51bca71d11b43783e5b4b1021095","tid":2293038,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"515883a4f95674b28d55a7524c1cedc7d2236fa9","tid":2293038,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:45:49.000Z","msg":"146票反對係暗共？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:50:22.000Z","msg":"黨友梗係要保駕護航啦"},{"pid":"1846c02bdcc2a61bb536d44352d49c6c8c33063d","tid":2293038,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4df4c60f2dc51bca71d11b43783e5b4b1021095","tid":2293038,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"515883a4f95674b28d55a7524c1cedc7d2236fa9","tid":2293038,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:45:49.000Z","msg":"146票反對係暗共？"},"citedBy":1,"rep